Greg,  I have successfully washed the beautiful plaid out of a '79 Westy on
cold and did not dry it...just pull it out of the washer and let it air dry. 
There were grease stains on mine and I pre-treated it with Dawn dishwashing
detergent and they all came out beautifully.  Greg T.



